# RBAC and Security

Use:
- role permission
- project membership permission
- device authorization

Roles:
- OWNER
- ADMIN
- FINANCE_MANAGER
- SUPERVISOR
- PIC
- FIELD_ENGINEER
- AUDITOR
- VIEWER

Sensitive actions require:
- permission
- reason
- confirmation
- audit log

Field engineer can only access assigned projects.
Auditor is read-only unless explicitly allowed.
Attachments must not be public by default.
